{
  "stem": "13673.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some things don't make any sense as I tell them, but this is how I remember it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, we went to the station, and my mother was allowed to come on the train with me as far as Wiesbaden.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's about, I'd say, about an hour on the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was early morning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my cousin was with me, my cousin Hilda, who's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who lived next door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you had a pretty close relationship with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She's three years older, so she was 14 at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I seem to remember that I was pretty alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, my mother was still with me for a little while anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Isn't it funny the things you remember?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had on a blue woolen dress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was wool, and I-- to this day, I'm allergic to wool.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But who knew from allergic in those days, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wore this blue dress, and I had underpants to match.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember an incident on that train where I had to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came out of it, everybody was pointing at me and laughing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I looked down, and I had my dress caught in my underpants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it, like, 60 years late-- no, not-- 50 years later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't have the whole train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not a special train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a regular passenger train, and we might have had one or two cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't say for sure, but there might have been about 100 kids on that train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were all very excited, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
